Time-Sensitive Logic.Unlock Time in Collect: The Collect function verifies that now > acc.unlockTime before allowing withdrawals, implementing a time-based restriction.

Conditional Logic Paths.Conditional Deposit Handling: The intitalized flag conditions the execution of SetMinSum and SetLogFile functions.
Conditional Logic Paths.Conditional Withdrawal Handling: The Collect function path depends on sufficient balance, minimum sum, and unlock time conditions being met.
